Package com.spnthreatviz

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bootstrap
    The main executable class.
    CVEObject
    A class representing a single CVE Object, holding all information important for ThreatViz.
    CVEParser
    The CVEParser class parses the NVD CVE files into POJOs and should be utilized when setting up the database.
    DataLoader
    Executable that loads the hardcoded NVD CVE file into a String and processes it.
    JsonFileReader
    File Reader Class that provides functionality to load the NVD CVE files (or any files really) into strings.
    JsonTransformer
    The Json Transformer class used for translating objects between front end JSON objects and back end POJOs.
    STVController
    Controller class used for API calls.
    STVException
    Container class for STV Exceptions.
    STVService
    Service class used by controller for basic functions of the application.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    STVException.CVEParsingException
    Exception thrown when there is an error parsing the NVD CVE files
    STVException.InvalidInputException
    Exception thrown when user input is invalid.
    STVException.MissingParametersException
    Exception thrown when user input is incomplete.
    STVException.STVServiceException
    General purpose exception.
